006package gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.model.util;
007
008import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.model.IChoiceGroupInstance;
009import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.model.IChoiceInstance;
010import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.model.INamedModelInstanceAbsolute;
011import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.model.INamedModelInstanceGrouped;
012
013import edu.umd.cs.findbugs.annotations.NonNull;
014
015public interface IDiagramNodeVisitor {
016  /**
017   * Handle an edge based on a {@link INamedModelInstanceAbsolute}.
018   *
019   * @param edge
020   *          the edge
021   */
022  void visit(@NonNull DefaultDiagramNode.ModelEdge edge);
023
024  /**
025   * Handle an edge based on a {@link INamedModelInstanceAbsolute} that is a
026   * member of a {@link IChoiceInstance}.
027   *
028   * @param edge
029   *          the edge
030   */
031  void visit(@NonNull DefaultDiagramNode.ChoiceEdge edge);
032
033  /**
034   * Handle an edge based on a {@link INamedModelInstanceGrouped} that is a member
035   * of a {@link IChoiceGroupInstance}.
036   *
037   * @param edge
038   *          the edge
039   */
040  void visit(@NonNull DefaultDiagramNode.ChoiceGroupEdge edge);
041}
